sequenceDiagram
    box Planning Team
    participant LD as Leaders (Tech Lead + PDM)
    end

    box Frontend Team (Workflow 03)
    participant Figma as Figma Design
    participant FigmaDev as figma-frontend-developer
    participant FrontExpert as frontend-expert (react / angular)
    participant CodeRevFE as code-reviewer
    participant MobileUX as mobile-ux-engineer
    participant DebugFE as debugger
    end

    participant Int as Integration

    %% PHASE 0: Input Delivery to Frontend Team
    Note over LD,DebugFE: PHASE 0: Planning Inputs Delivery to Frontend Team

    LD->>Figma: Deliver HUs and UI requirements
    LD->>FigmaDev: Deliver HUs and requirements
    LD->>FrontExpert: Deliver HUs and requirements
    Note right of LD: All team members receive:<br/>- HUs breakdown<br/>- UI/UX requirements<br/>- Acceptance criteria<br/>- Estimated effort

    %% PHASE 1: Frontend Development - Figma (6h)
    Note over Figma,DebugFE: PHASE 1: Frontend Development - Figma (6h)

    Figma->>FigmaDev: Figma design file URL

    activate FigmaDev
    Note right of FigmaDev: Figma MCP:<br/>- get_file_data()<br/>- get_variables()<br/>- Extract tokens<br/>- Generate components
    FigmaDev->>FrontExpert: React/Angular components + types
    deactivate FigmaDev

    activate FrontExpert
    Note right of FrontExpert: Specialized agents (React / Angular):<br/>- Interfaces & Props types<br/>- Hooks / RxJS<br/>- State management<br/>- WebSocket client<br/>- API integration
    FrontExpert-->>CodeRevFE: Type-safe code
    deactivate FrontExpert

    activate CodeRevFE
    Note right of CodeRevFE: Review:<br/>- Security (XSS)<br/>- Performance<br/>- Accessibility<br/>- Best practices
    CodeRevFE-->>MobileUX: ✓ Code approved
    deactivate CodeRevFE

    activate MobileUX
    Note right of MobileUX: Test responsive:<br/>- Mobile 320px<br/>- Tablet 768px<br/>- Desktop 1024px<br/>- Screenshots (Playwright)
    MobileUX-->>DebugFE: ✓ Responsive
    deactivate MobileUX

    activate DebugFE
    Note right of DebugFE: - Fix React/Angular warnings<br/>- Memory leaks<br/>- WebSocket logic<br/>- UI bugs
    DebugFE-->>Int: ✓ Frontend ready
    deactivate DebugFE

    %% PHASE 2: Integration Output
    Note over Int: PHASE 2: Integration Output

    activate Int
    Note right of Int: Integration delivers:<br/>- Swagger / OpenAPI API documentation URL<br/>- Unit tests (frontend + API)<br/>- E2E test reports<br/>- Build & deploy artifacts
    Int-->>LD: Swagger + OpenAPI API URL + Unit tests
    deactivate Int
